text: Oh my, are you OK? Forcing through motion sickness is guaranteed to have a bad day afterwards... take a break if you start feeling sick and continue only if you feel good enough. What help when playing VR: cooling down a bit with a fan, taking breaks, drinking water (people say ginger ale is effective). Start VR with easy teleportation games (like Gal Gun 2 VR), most games have an option for that, like HL Alyx, MC too. VR doesn't work that way. The headsets have a fixed FOV. Minecraft might still have a fov slider, but you would probably get more sick if it didn't match your natural vision in VR.
